---
title: "State Machine - Salary Adjustment Session"
config:
  theme: neutral
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> MenuDisplayed
    MenuDisplayed --> EnteringCode : option 2/3 selected
    EnteringCode --> EnteringAmount : code entered
    EnteringAmount --> Validating : amount entered
    Validating --> Failed : code not found /<br>amount <= 0 /<br>salary after <= 0
    Validating --> Adjusting : all rules pass
    Adjusting --> HistorySaved : salary updated
    HistorySaved --> Succeeded
    Succeeded --> MenuDisplayed : back to menu
    Failed --> MenuDisplayed : error shown,<br>back to menu
    MenuDisplayed --> [*] : option 5 (Quit)
